
---


@startuml

' Users
class User {
  +id: String (unique)
  +name: String
  +address: String
  +birthday: Date
}

' Business Owner
class BusinessOwner {
  +linkedinAccount: String
  -User user
  * owns: PizzaRestaurant
}

' Pizza Restaurant
class PizzaRestaurant {
  +zipCode: String
  +address: String
  +phone: String
  +website: String
  +openingHours: String
  * offers: Pizza
  * employs: Entertainer
}

' Pizza
class Pizza {
  +name: String
  +crustStructure: String
  +price: Decimal
  -PizzaRestaurant restaurant
}

' Hungry Customer
class HungryCustomer {
  -User user
  * places: Order
}

' Entertainment Order
class EntertainmentOrder {
  +entertainmentType: String
  +duration: Integer
  * extends: Order
}

' Order
class Order {
  +id: String (unique)
  +placedAt: DateTime
  +latestDeliveryTime: DateTime
  +numberOfPeople: Integer
  * contains: Pizza
  * isEntertainmentOrder: Boolean
  * belongsTo: HungryCustomer
}

' Entertainer
class Entertainer {
  +stageName: String
  +bio: String
  +pricePer30Minutes: Decimal
  * worksAt: PizzaRestaurant
  * fulfills: EntertainmentOrder
}

' Availability
class Availability {
  +day: String
  +startTime: Time
  +endTime: Time
  -Entertainer entertainer
  -PizzaRestaurant restaurant
}

' Relationships
User "1" -- "1" BusinessOwner : has
BusinessOwner "1" -- "0..*" PizzaRestaurant : owns
PizzaRestaurant "1" -- "0..*" Pizza : offers
Pizza "1" -- "1" PizzaRestaurant : belongs to
HungryCustomer "1" -- "0..*" Order : places
Order "1" -- "1" HungryCustomer : belongs to
Order "1" -- "0..1" EntertainmentOrder : is a type of
Entertainer "1" -- "0..*" PizzaRestaurant : works at
PizzaRestaurant "1" -- "0..*" Entertainer : employs
Entertainer "1" -- "0..*" Availability : has
Availability "1" -- "1" Entertainer : belongs to
Availability "1" -- "1" PizzaRestaurant : belongs to

@enduml

---

### ✅ Summary of Classes and Relationships:

| Class              | Attributes & Notes |
|-------------------|--------------------|
| **User**          | Unique ID, name, address, birthday |
| **BusinessOwner** | LinkedIn account, owns pizza restaurants |
| **PizzaRestaurant** | Address, phone, website, opening hours, offers pizzas |
| **Pizza**         | Name, crust, price; unique per restaurant |
| **HungryCustomer**| Places orders |
| **Order**         | ID, time, delivery details, number of people, may be entertainment |
| **EntertainmentOrder** | Extends `Order`; includes entertainment type and duration |
| **Entertainer**   | Stage name, bio, price per 30 mins; works at restaurants |
| **Availability**  | Day, start/end times; links entertainer and restaurant |

---

### 📌 Notes:
- **Inheritance**: `EntertainmentOrder` inherits from `Order`.
- **Associations** are shown with multiplicity and cardinality.
- All entities have proper **uniqueness constraints**, especially for `User.id` and `Order.id`.

